# Frontend API URL Configuration

## Local Development
# Your backend must be running on localhost:4000
# VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:4000

## Production (Vercel Deployment)
# IMPORTANT: Set this in Vercel Project Settings > Environment Variables
# Do NOT commit production URLs to git!
# Examples:
# VITE_API_URL=https://swigato-backend.vercel.app
# VITE_API_URL=https://api.swigato.com
# VITE_API_URL=https://your-backend-domain.com

# For local development, use:
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:4000
